=head1 NAME

130-send.0.mdl

=head1 DEPENDS

libraries:

 CVML
 Secure::image
 TOM::Utils::datetime

3rd party libraries:

 MIME::Base64
 Digest::MD5  qw(md5 md5_hex md5_base64)
